body: Thanks for the report @guillaumekln -- it doesn't appear that those particular functions have changed recently, at least not since ~April when support for nested structures was added, but it's easy to imagine that changes in while loops or similar had an unexpected effect. @guptapriya , could this be related to changes you made on 07/03 [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.9/tensorflow/python/ops/control_flow_ops.py#L3209)?
